  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\"Raven-feeder\" redirects here. For the ship, see <a href=\"/index.php/Ravenfeeder\" title=\"Ravenfeeder\">Ravenfeeder</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Drumm\" title=\"House Drumm\"><img alt=\"House Drumm.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/50px-House_Drumm.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/75px-House_Drumm.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/100px-House_Drumm.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Regnar Drumm<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Raven-feeder</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Drumm\" title=\"House Drumm\"><img alt=\"House Drumm.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/50px-House_Drumm.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/75px-House_Drumm.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/100px-House_Drumm.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nRegnar Drumm</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"High King of the Iron Islands\">High King of the Iron Islands</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rock_king\" title=\"Rock king\">Rock king</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Wyk\" title=\"Old Wyk\">Old Wyk</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Predecessor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Erich_I_Greyiron\" title=\"Erich I Greyiron\">Erich I Greyiron</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nRaven-feeder</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">Ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Drumm\" title=\"House Drumm\">House Drumm</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Regnar Drumm</b>, known as <b>Raven-feeder</b>, was a <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"High King of the Iron Islands\">High King of the Iron Islands</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Drumm\" title=\"House Drumm\">House Drumm</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Regnar_Drumm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Erich_I_Greyiron\" title=\"Erich I Greyiron\">Erich I Greyiron</a> seized the crown of his father, <a href=\"/index.php/Urras_Greyiron\" title=\"Urras Greyiron\">Urras Greyiron</a>, upon Ironfoot's death and declared himself <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"High King of the Iron Islands\">High King of the Iron Islands</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Galon_Whitestaff\" title=\"Galon Whitestaff\">Galon Whitestaff</a> commanded that kings may only be made by <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot\" title=\"Kingsmoot\">kingsmoot</a>, however, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> captains and kings cast Erich down from power. Regnar, the <a href=\"/index.php/Rock_king\" title=\"Rock king\">rock king</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Wyk\" title=\"Old Wyk\">Old Wyk</a>, was chosen the new High King at the kingsmoot.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Regnar_Drumm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands: Driftwood Crowns.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Erich_I_Greyiron\" title=\"Erich I Greyiron\">Erich I Greyiron</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>3rd <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"High King of the Iron Islands\">High King of the Iron Islands</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\"><b>Unknown </b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403223640\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.090 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.302 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 912/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 13758/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8509/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 998/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 667/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.61 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  289.980      1 -total\n 76.82%  222.759      1 Template:Infobox_monarch\n 76.05%  220.526      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.39%   33.021      1 Template:Redirect\n 10.85%   31.462     14 Template:Infobox_value\n  7.48%   21.683      1 Template:S-bef\n  6.19%   17.943      3 Template:Main_other\n  5.30%   15.358      1 Template:S-bef/check\n  4.86%   14.095      5 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.60%    4.632      1 Template:S-ttl\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:19168-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403223640 and revision id 308956\n -->\n",
